<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-10-21T11:25:03-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-10-21T11:25:03-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-21T11:25:03-04:00</updated><title>您可以将 YouTube Music 设置为 Apple HomePod 上的默认服务</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;背景为几何设计的 YouTube 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OUzBKyEGrWj8j1MzCAUonilH_N0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/72779486/acastro_STK092_04.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;WS2MwN&quot;>;对于少数苹果用户来说是个好消息使用 YouTube Music 的家庭用户（我知道您在场！） — 您现在可以将该服务与您的 HomePods 集成，并要求 Siri 使用 YouTube Music 播放歌曲，或者将该服务设置为您的默认来源。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://9to5google.com/2023/10/20/youtube-music-homepod/&quot;>;&lt;em>;9to5Google&lt;/em>;发现&lt;/a>; YouTube Music 产品负责人 Brandon Bilinski 发布的 Reddit 帖子&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/YoutubeMusic/comments/17cht03/you_can_now_use_youtube_music_on_your_apple/?utm_source=share&amp;amp;utm_medium=web3x&amp;amp;utm_name=web3xcss&amp;amp;utm_term=1&amp;amp;utm_content=share_button&quot;>;宣布更新&lt;/a>;。您可以找到 &lt;a href=&quot;https://support.google.com/youtubemusic/answer/9231765?hl=en&amp;amp;co=GENIE.Platform%3DiOS#zippy=%2Capple-homepod:~:text=You%20can %20use%20YouTube%20Music%20on%20smart%20speakers%2C&quot;>;服务支持页面上的集成设置说明&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aLgcXp&quot;>;第三个列表- 可以与 HomePods 集成的派对音乐服务仍然非常精简。到目前为止，添加了支持的 Apple Music 最大替代品可能是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/5/6/22422637/apple-homepod-mini-deezer-third-party -music-integration&quot;>;Deezer&lt;/a>; 和潘多拉。您可以&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/21/23883860/siri-can-now-play-spotify-on-apple-homepod-smart-speaker&quot;>;最后要求 Siri在 HomePods 上使用 Spotify 播放音乐&lt;/a>;，但该公司仍然...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/21/23926378/youtube- music-apple-homepod-third-party-support-default-service&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/21/23926378/youtube-music-apple-homepod-third-party-support-default-service" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/21/23926378/youtube-music-apple-homepod-third-party-support-default-service</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-21T11:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-21T11:00:00-04:00</updated><title>曼杜布以令人兴奋的方式揭示了沙特阿拉伯零工经济中生存的危险</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一个留着小胡子的男人，穿着黄色毛衣和黑色皮夹克。男人背着一个穿着白色毛衣的年轻女孩，两人在狂欢节上站在一起。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AibUzIN8BpAutPh-N5hVDX3K6NM=/288x136:2871x1858/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72779442/NCF_TIFF01_SAWSAN_2023080 2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由多伦多国际电影节提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;导演 Ali Kalthami 的处女作《Mandoob》以迷人的方式展现了沙特阿拉伯的拼车和送货司机的世界。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23925562/mandoob-review-ali-kalthami&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23925562/mandoob-review-ali-kalthami" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23925562/mandoob-review-ali-kalthami</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-21T10:14:35-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-21T10:14:35-04:00</updated><title>微软和任天堂将在万圣节期间大幅降价许多恐怖游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;暗黑破坏神 IV 的屏幕截图，天使伊纳留斯 (Inarius) 从高处降临，翅膀是光的卷须&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AfCRYML-xy9i0j9vXBOXSVOF-JM =/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72779336/diablo_iv_review_hed__1_.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;暗黑破坏神 IV&lt;em>;，